{
  "an1.258:0.1": "Aṅguttara Nikāya 1 ",
  "an1.258:0.2": "20. Sattamavagga ",
  "an1.258-267:1.1": "\"Etadaggaṁ, bhikkhave, mama sāvikānaṁ upāsikānaṁ paṭhamaṁ saraṇaṁ gacchantīnaṁ yadidaṁ sujātā seniyadhītā.\n(1)",
  "an1.258-267:1.2": "…   Dāyikānaṁ yadidaṁ visākhā migāramātā.\n(2)",
  "an1.258-267:1.3": "…   Bahussutānaṁ yadidaṁ khujjuttarā.\n(3)",
  "an1.258-267:1.4": "…   Mettāvihārīnaṁ yadidaṁ sāmāvatī.\n(4)",
  "an1.258-267:1.5": "…   Jhāyīnaṁ yadidaṁ uttarānandamātā.\n(5)",
  "an1.258-267:1.6": "…   Paṇītadāyikānaṁ yadidaṁ suppavāsā koliyadhītā.\n(6)",
  "an1.258-267:1.7": "…   Gilānupaṭṭhākīnaṁ yadidaṁ suppiyā upāsikā.\n(7)",
  "an1.258-267:1.8": "…   Aveccappasannānaṁ yadidaṁ kātiyānī.\n(8)",
  "an1.258-267:1.9": "…   Vissāsikānaṁ yadidaṁ nakulamātā gahapatānī.\n(9)",
  "an1.258-267:1.10": "…   Anussavappasannānaṁ yadidaṁ kāḷī upāsikā kuraragharikā\"ti.\n(10)\nVaggo sattamo.\n(Etadaggavaggo niṭṭhito.)\nSattamavagga"
}